        <mxCell id="Xab4sQG90tsSxLUxtWYE-2" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;#21&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Write a program to calculate circle area a long the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;circumference, than print it&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;on the screen&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;area =&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 20pt; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;l&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;/&amp;nbsp;4.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 26.6667px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;π&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-language:AR-YE&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;1. Ask the user enter l&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;2. pi = 3.14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;3. area = (l * l ) / (4 * pi)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;4. Print area&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeWidth=5;perimeterSpacing=6;strokeColor=default;" parent="1" vertex="1">
